sections.text:
Deleterious SNPs with missense consequence in the human TOP2A gene were extracted from the ENSEMBL Variation resources [150] accessed from https://www.ensembl. org/Homo_sapiens/Gene/Variation_Gene/Table?db=core;g=ENSG00000131747;r=17:4038 8525-40417896, 9 March 2023. Strict filtering criteria were used: SIFT [151] score ≤ 0.05;
Int. J. Mol. Sci. 2023, 24, 10740 21 of 27
PolyPhen [152] ≥0.95; REVEL [153] ≥0.65; and Mutation Assessor [154] score ≥ 0.9. Only SNPs meeting all criteria at the same time were chosen as highly deleterious ones.
